sqlReaderQuery.value:
Select 
       it1.DATAAREAID
     , it1.ITEMID
     , it1.PRODUCT
     , it1.ABCVALUE
     , it1.COSTGROUPID
     , it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION
     , it1.CREATEDDATETIME
     , it1.MODIFIEDDATETIME
     , da1.TIMEZONE                     as DATAAREA_TIMEZONE
     , e1.PRODUCT                       as ECORESPRODUCTTRANSLATION_PRODUCT
     , e1.NAME                          as ECORESPRODUCTTRANSLATION_NAME
     , e1.MODIFIEDDATETIME              as ECORESPRODUCTTRANSLATION_MODIFIEDDATETIME
     , bcg1.DATAAREAID                  as BOMCOSTGROUP_DATAAREAID
     , bcg1.COSTGROUPID                 as BOMCOSTGROUP_COSTGROUPID
     , bcg1.NAME                        as BOMCOSTGROUP_NAME
     , bcg1.COSTGROUPBEHAVIOR           as BOMCOSTGROUP_COSTGROUPBEHAVIOR
     , bcg1.COSTGROUPTYPE               as BOMCOSTGROUP_COSTGROUPTYPE
     , bcg1.TYPEDEFAULT                 as BOMCOSTGROUP_TYPEDEFAULT
     , E_CATEGORY                       as DEFAULTDIMENSION_E_CATEGORY
     , E_CATEGORY_DESCRIPTION_PARENT    as DEFAULTDIMENSION_E_CATEGORY_DESCRIPTION_PARENT
     , E_CATEGORY_DESCRIPTION           as DEFAULTDIMENSION_E_CATEGORY_DESCRIPTION
     , F_FAMILY                         as DEFAULTDIMENSION_F_FAMILY
     , F_FAMILY_DESCRIPTION             as DEFAULTDIMENSION_F_FAMILY_DESCRIPTION
     , DEFAULTDIMENSION_MODIFIEDDATETIME
     , tzi1.TIMEZONEID                  as TIMEZONEINFO_TIMEZONEID
     , tzi1.STARTDATE                   as TIMEZONEINFO_STARTDATE
     , tzi1.ENDDATE                     as TIMEZONEINFO_ENDDATE
     , tzi1.TIMEBIAS                    as TIMEZONEINFO_TIMEBIAS
     , itm1.MODULETYPE                  as INVENTTABLEMODULE_MODULETYPE
     , itm1.DATAAREAID                  as INVENTTABLEMODULE_DATAAREAID
     , itm1.ITEMID                      as INVENTTABLEMODULE_ITEMID
     , itm1.UNITID                      as INVENTTABLEMODULE_UNITID
     , uom1.RECID                       as UNITOFMEASURE_RECID
     , uom1.SYMBOL                      as UNITOFMEASURE_SYMBOL
     , uom1.MODIFIEDDATETIME            as UNITOFMEASURE_MODIFIEDDATETIME
     , uomt1.UNITOFMEASURE              as UNITOFMEASURETRANSLATION_UNITOFMEASURE
     , uomt1.DESCRIPTION                as UNITOFMEASURETRANSLATION_DESCRIPTION
     , uomt1.MODIFIEDDATETIME           as UNITOFMEASURETRANSLATION_MODIFIEDDATETIME
     , brand1.DISPLAYPRODUCTNUMBER      as TSIPHITEM_DISPLAYPRODUCTNUMBER
     , brand1.BASEITEMID                as TSIPHITEM_BASEITEMID
     , brand1.PRODSIZE                  as TSIPHITEM_PRODSIZE
     , brand1.PGCID                     as TSIPHBASEITEM_PGCID
     , brand1.BASEITEMDESCRIPTION       as TSIPHBASEITEM_BASEITEMDESCRIPTION
     , brand1.DEFAULTFDNHIGH            as TSIPHBASEITEM_DEFAULTFDNHIGH
     , brand1.DEFAULTFDNLOW             as TSIPHBASEITEM_DEFAULTFDNLOW
     , brand1.DEFAULTFDNMED             as TSIPHBASEITEM_DEFAULTFDNMED
     , brand1.PIECETYPEID               as TSIPHBASEITEM_PIECETYPEID
     , brand1.PRICECOLLECTIONID         as TSIPHBASEITEM_PRICECOLLECTIONID
     , brand1.PLEVELID                  as TSIPHGROUP_PLEVELID
     , brand1.PGCDESC                   as TSIPHGROUP_PGCDESC
     , brand1.TPG_ISACTIVE              as TSIPHGROUP_ISACTIVE
     , brand1.EFFECTIVEDATE             as TSIPHGROUP_EFFECTIVEDATE
     , brand1.EXPIRATIONDATE            as TSIPHGROUP_EXPIRATIONDATE
     , brand1.MSTRPGCID                 as TSIPHGROUP_MSTRPGCID
     , brand1.COMFORTID                 as TSIPHGROUP_COMFORTID
     , brand1.CONSTRUCTID               as TSIPHGROUP_CONSTRUCTID
     , brand1.LINELAUNCHID              as TSIPHLEVEL_LINELAUNCHID
     , brand1.YOYID                     as TSIPHLEVEL_YOYID
     , brand1.PLEVELDESC                as TSIPHLEVEL_PLEVELDESC
     , brand1.TPL_ISACTIVE              as TSIPHLEVEL_ISACTIVE
     , brand1.ISSPECIALTY               as TSIPHLEVEL_ISSPECIALTY
     , brand1.TYPEID                    as TSIPHYEAROVERYEAR_TYPEID
     , brand1.PRICEBANDID               as TSIPHYEAROVERYEAR_PRICEBANDID
     , brand1.YOYDESC                   as TSIPHYEAROVERYEAR_YOYDESC
     , brand1.STYLEID                   as TSIPHTYPE_STYLEID
     , brand1.TECHNOLOGYID              as TSIPHTYPE_TECHNOLOGYID
     , brand1.TYPEDESC                  as TSIPHTYPE_TYPEDESC
     , brand1.BRANDID                   as TSIPHSTYLE_BRANDID
     , brand1.STYLEDESC                 as TSIPHSTYLE_STYLEDESC
     , brand1.MBRANDID                  as TSIPHBRAND_MBRANDID
     , brand1.BRANDDESC                 as TSIPHBRAND_BRANDDESC
     , brand1.MBRANDDESC                as TSIPHMASTERBRAND_MBRANDDESC
     , brand1.TECHNOLOGYDESC            as TSIPHTECHNOLOGY_TECHNOLOGYDESC
     , brand1.PRICEBAND                 as TSIPHPRICEBAND_PRICEBAND
     , brand1.LINELAUNCHDESC            as TSIPHLINELAUNCH_LINELAUNCHDESC
     , brand1.COMFORTDESC               as TSIPHCOMFORT_COMFORTDESC
     , brand1.CONSTRUCTDESC             as TSIPHCONSTRUCTION_CONSTRUCTDESC
     , brand1.PRICECOLLECTIONDESC       as TSIPHPRICECOLLECTION_PRICECOLLECTIONDESC
     , brand1.SIZEID                    as TPSSIZE_SIZEID
     , brand1.DIMENSIONS                as TPSSIZE_DIMENSIONS
     , brand1.EBCPANELLENGTH            as TPSSIZE_EBCPANELLENGTH
     , brand1.EBCPANELWIDTH             as TPSSIZE_EBCPANELWIDTH
     , brand1.ACTIVE                    as TPSSIZE_ACTIVE
     , (
           SELECT MAX(LastUpdateDate)
            FROM
            (
                VALUES
                    (
                        it1.MODIFIEDDATETIME
                    )
                  , (
                        isnull(   e1.MODIFIEDDATETIME
                                , '1950-01-01'
                              )
                    )
                  , (
                        isnull(   uom1.MODIFIEDDATETIME
                                , '1950-01-01'
                              )
                    )
                  , (
                        isnull(   uomt1.MODIFIEDDATETIME
                                , '1950-01-01'
                              )
                    )
            ) AS UpdateDate ( LastUpdateDate )
       )                                AS LAST_MODIFIEDDATETIME
     , convert(   varchar (max)
                , brand1.ITEM_HIERARCHY_HASH_KEY
                , 2
              )                         as ITEM_HIERARCHY_HASH_KEY
     , row_number() over ( partition by brand1.DISPLAYPRODUCTNUMBER
                                      , brand1.BASEITEMID
                                      , brand1.PRODSIZE
                                      , brand1.PGCID
                                      , brand1.BASEITEMDESCRIPTION
                                      , brand1.DEFAULTFDNHIGH
                                      , brand1.DEFAULTFDNLOW
                                      , brand1.DEFAULTFDNMED
                                      , brand1.PIECETYPEID
                                      , brand1.PRICECOLLECTIONID
                                      , brand1.PLEVELID
                                      , brand1.PGCDESC
                                      , brand1.TPG_ISACTIVE
                                      , brand1.EFFECTIVEDATE
                                      , brand1.EXPIRATIONDATE
                                      , brand1.MSTRPGCID
                                      , brand1.COMFORTID
                                      , brand1.CONSTRUCTID
                                      , brand1.LINELAUNCHID
                                      , brand1.YOYID
                                      , brand1.PLEVELDESC
                                      , brand1.TPL_ISACTIVE
                                      , brand1.ISSPECIALTY
                                      , brand1.TYPEID
                                      , brand1.PRICEBANDID
                                      , brand1.YOYDESC
                                      , brand1.STYLEID
                                      , brand1.TECHNOLOGYID
                                      , brand1.TYPEDESC
                                      , brand1.BRANDID
                                      , brand1.STYLEDESC
                                      , brand1.MBRANDID
                                      , brand1.BRANDDESC
                                      , brand1.MBRANDDESC
                                      , brand1.TECHNOLOGYDESC
                                      , brand1.PRICEBAND
                                      , brand1.LINELAUNCHDESC
                                      , brand1.COMFORTDESC
                                      , brand1.CONSTRUCTDESC
                                      , brand1.PRICECOLLECTIONDESC
                                      , brand1.SIZEID
                                      , brand1.DIMENSIONS
                                      , brand1.EBCPANELLENGTH
                                      , brand1.EBCPANELWIDTH
                                      , brand1.ACTIVE
                                      , brand1.ITEM_HIERARCHY_HASH_KEY
                           order by
                               (
                                   SELECT MAX(LastUpdateDate)
                                    FROM
                                    (
                                        VALUES
                                            (
                                                it1.MODIFIEDDATETIME
                                            )
                                          , (
                                                isnull(   e1.MODIFIEDDATETIME
                                                        , '1950-01-01'
                                                      )
                                            )
                                          , (
                                                isnull(   uom1.MODIFIEDDATETIME
                                                        , '1950-01-01'
                                                      )
                                            )
                                          , (
                                                isnull(   uomt1.MODIFIEDDATETIME
                                                        , '1950-01-01'
                                                      )
                                            )
                                    ) AS UpdateDate ( LastUpdateDate )
                               ) DESC
                         )              as BRAND_RANK
     , iig1.itemgroupid                 As ITEMGROUPID
	 , iig1.itemgroupname				As ITEMGROUPNAME
 From
    dbo.INVENTTABLE            it1
     left join
     (
         Select iigi.ITEMGROUPID As itemgroupid
              , iig.Name As itemgroupname
			  , iigi.itemid
			  , iigi.ITEMDATAAREAID
          FROM
             dbo.INVENTITEMGROUP          iig
              Inner Join
                  dbo.INVENTITEMGROUPITEM iigi
              On
                  iig.ITEMGROUPID = iigi.ITEMGROUPID
                  And iig.DATAAREAID = iigi.ITEMGROUPDATAAREAID
     )                         iig1
     ON
         it1.ITEMID = iig1.ITEMID
         and it1.DATAAREAID = iig1.ITEMDATAAREAID
     left join
     (
         select d10.ID
              , d10.TIMEZONE
          from
             dbo.DATAAREA                                                          d10
              inner join
              ( select ID, max(RECID) as MAX_RECID from dbo.DATAAREA group by ID ) d11
              on
                  d10.ID = d11.ID
                  and d10.RECID = d11.MAX_RECID
     )                         da1
     on
         it1.DATAAREAID = da1.ID
     left join
     (
         select e10.PRODUCT
              , e10.NAME
              , e10.MODIFIEDDATETIME
          from
             dbo.ECORESPRODUCTTRANSLATION e10
              inner join
              (
                  select PRODUCT
                       , max(MODIFIEDDATETIME) as MAX_MODIFIEDDATETIME
                   from
                      dbo.ECORESPRODUCTTRANSLATION
                   where
                      LANGUAGEID = 'en-us'
                   group by
                      PRODUCT
              )                           e11
              on
                  e10.PRODUCT = e11.PRODUCT
                  and e10.MODIFIEDDATETIME = e11.MAX_MODIFIEDDATETIME
          where
             LANGUAGEID = 'en-us'
     )                         e1
     on
         it1.PRODUCT = e1.PRODUCT
     left join
         dbo.BOMCOSTGROUP      bcg1
     on
         it1.DATAAREAID = bcg1.DATAAREAID
         and it1.COSTGROUPID = bcg1.COSTGROUPID
     left join
     (
         select distinct
                it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION
              , max(   case
                           when da1.NAME = 'E_Category'
                               then davsi1.DISPLAYVALUE
                           else null
                       end
                   ) over ( partition by it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION ) as E_CATEGORY
              , max(   case
                           when da1.NAME = 'F_Family'
                               then davsi1.DISPLAYVALUE
                           else null
                       end
                   ) over ( partition by it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION ) as F_FAMILY
              , max(   case
                           when da1.NAME = 'E_Category'
                                and davsi1.DISPLAYVALUE in
                              (
                                  '10'
                                , '11'
                                , '20'
                                , '50'
                                , '60'
                              )
                               then desc1.DESCRIPTION
                           when da1.NAME = 'E_Category'
                               then 'Other'
                           else null
                       end
                   ) over ( partition by it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION ) as E_CATEGORY_DESCRIPTION_PARENT
              -- use MIN because you want the first iteration of the character set
              , min(   case
                           when da1.NAME = 'E_Category'
                               then desc1.DESCRIPTION
                           else null
                       end
                   ) over ( partition by it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION ) as E_CATEGORY_DESCRIPTION
              , min(   case
                           when da1.NAME = 'F_Family'
                               then desc1.DESCRIPTION
                           else null
                       end
                   ) over ( partition by it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION ) as F_FAMILY_DESCRIPTION
              , max((
                        select max(i)
                         from
                         (
                             values
                                 (
                                     davsi1.MODIFIEDDATETIME
                                 )
                               , (
                                     dav1.MODIFIEDDATETIME
                                 )
                               , (
                                     da1.MODIFIEDDATETIME
                                 )
                               , (
                                     desc1.DESC_MODIFIEDDATETIME
                                 )
                         ) AS T ( i )
                    )
                   ) over ( partition by it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION ) as DEFAULTDIMENSION_MODIFIEDDATETIME
          from
          ( select distinct DEFAULTDIMENSION from dbo.INVENTTABLE ) it1
              left join
                  dbo.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESETITEM                davsi1
              on
                  it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION = davsi1.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESET
              left join
                  dbo.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE                       dav1
              on
                  davsi1.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE = dav1.RECID
              left join
                  dbo.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE                            da1
              on
                  dav1.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE = da1.RECID
              left join
              (
                  select dft1.VALUE
                       , da2.NAME
                       , dft1.DESCRIPTION
                       , (
                             select max(i)
                              from
                              (
                                  values
                                      (
                                          dft1.MODIFIEDDATETIME
                                      )
                                    , (
                                          dadc1.MODIFIEDDATETIME
                                      )
                                    , (
                                          da2.MODIFIEDDATETIME
                                      )
                              ) AS T ( i )
                         ) as DESC_MODIFIEDDATETIME
                   from
                      dbo.DIMENSIONFINANCIALTAG              dft1
                       left join
                           dbo.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEDIRCATEGORY dadc1
                       on
                           dft1.FINANCIALTAGCATEGORY = dadc1.DIRCATEGORY
                       left join
                           dbo.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE            da2
                       on
                           dadc1.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE = da2.RECID
              )                                                     desc1
              on
                  davsi1.DISPLAYVALUE = desc1.VALUE
                  and da1.NAME = desc1.NAME
     )                         def1
     on
         it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION = def1.DEFAULTDIMENSION
     left join
         dbo.TIMEZONEINFO      tzi1
     on
         da1.TIMEZONE = tzi1.TIMEZONEID
         and it1.CREATEDDATETIME >= tzi1.STARTDATE
         and it1.CREATEDDATETIME < tzi1.ENDDATE
     left join
         dbo.INVENTTABLEMODULE itm1
     on
         itm1.MODULETYPE = 1
         and it1.DATAAREAID = itm1.DATAAREAID
         and it1.ITEMID = itm1.ITEMID
     left join
     (
         select uom10.RECID
              , uom10.SYMBOL
              , uom10.MODIFIEDDATETIME
          from
             dbo.UNITOFMEASURE uom10
              inner join
              (
                  select SYMBOL
                       , max(MODIFIEDDATETIME) as MAX_MODIFIEDDATETIME
                   from
                      dbo.UNITOFMEASURE
                   group by
                      SYMBOL
              )                uom11
              on
                  uom10.SYMBOL = uom11.SYMBOL
                  and uom10.MODIFIEDDATETIME = uom11.MAX_MODIFIEDDATETIME
     )                         uom1
     on
         itm1.UNITID = uom1.SYMBOL
     left join
     (
         select uomt10.UNITOFMEASURE
              , uomt10.DESCRIPTION
              , uomt10.MODIFIEDDATETIME
          from
             dbo.UNITOFMEASURETRANSLATION uomt10
              inner join
              (
                  select UNITOFMEASURE
                       , max(MODIFIEDDATETIME) as MAX_MODIFIEDDATETIME
                   from
                      dbo.UNITOFMEASURETRANSLATION
                   where
                      LANGUAGEID = 'en-us'
                   group by
                      UNITOFMEASURE
              )                           uomt11
              on
                  uomt10.UNITOFMEASURE = uomt11.UNITOFMEASURE
                  and uomt10.MODIFIEDDATETIME = uomt11.MAX_MODIFIEDDATETIME
          where
             uomt10.LANGUAGEID = 'en-us'
     )                         uomt1
     on
         uom1.RECID = uomt1.UNITOFMEASURE
     left join
     (
         select distinct
                tpi1.DISPLAYPRODUCTNUMBER
              , tpi1.BASEITEMID
              , tpi1.PRODSIZE
              , tpbi1.PGCID
              , tpbi1.BASEITEMDESCRIPTION
              , tpbi1.DEFAULTFDNHIGH
              , tpbi1.DEFAULTFDNLOW
              , tpbi1.DEFAULTFDNMED
              , tpbi1.PIECETYPEID
              , tpbi1.PRICECOLLECTIONID
              , tpg1.PLEVELID
              , tpg1.PGCDESC
              , tpg1.ISACTIVE as TPG_ISACTIVE
              , tpg1.EFFECTIVEDATE
              , tpg1.EXPIRATIONDATE
              , tpg1.MSTRPGCID
              , tpg1.COMFORTID
              , tpg1.CONSTRUCTID
              , tpl1.LINELAUNCHID
              , tpl1.YOYID
              , tpl1.PLEVELDESC
              , tpl1.ISACTIVE as TPL_ISACTIVE
              , tpl1.ISSPECIALTY
              , tpyoy1.TYPEID
              , tpyoy1.PRICEBANDID
              , tpyoy1.YOYDESC
              , tpt1.STYLEID
              , tpt1.TECHNOLOGYID
              , tpt1.TYPEDESC
              , tps1.BRANDID
              , tps1.STYLEDESC
              , tpb1.MBRANDID
              , tpb1.BRANDDESC
              , tpmb1.MBRANDDESC
              , tptech1.TECHNOLOGYDESC
              , tppb1.PRICEBAND
              , tpll1.LINELAUNCHDESC
              , tpc1.COMFORTDESC
              , tpcon1.CONSTRUCTDESC
              , tppc1.PRICECOLLECTIONDESC
              , ts1.SIZEID
              , ts1.DIMENSIONS
              , ts1.EBCPANELLENGTH
              , ts1.EBCPANELWIDTH
              , ts1.ACTIVE
              , hashbytes(   'SHA2_256'
                           , concat(   tpi1.DISPLAYPRODUCTNUMBER
                                     , tpi1.BASEITEMID
                                     , tpi1.PRODSIZE
                                     , tpbi1.PGCID
                                     , tpbi1.BASEITEMDESCRIPTION
                                     , tpbi1.DEFAULTFDNHIGH
                                     , tpbi1.DEFAULTFDNLOW
                                     , tpbi1.DEFAULTFDNMED
                                     , tpbi1.PIECETYPEID
                                     , tpbi1.PRICECOLLECTIONID
                                     , tpg1.PLEVELID
                                     , tpg1.PGCDESC
                                     , tpg1.ISACTIVE
                                     , tpg1.EFFECTIVEDATE
                                     , tpg1.EXPIRATIONDATE
                                     , tpg1.MSTRPGCID
                                     , tpg1.COMFORTID
                                     , tpg1.CONSTRUCTID
                                     , tpl1.LINELAUNCHID
                                     , tpl1.YOYID
                                     , tpl1.PLEVELDESC
                                     , tpl1.ISACTIVE
                                     , tpl1.ISSPECIALTY
                                     , tpyoy1.TYPEID
                                     , tpyoy1.PRICEBANDID
                                     , tpyoy1.YOYDESC
                                     , tpt1.STYLEID
                                     , tpt1.TECHNOLOGYID
                                     , tpt1.TYPEDESC
                                     , tps1.BRANDID
                                     , tps1.STYLEDESC
                                     , tpb1.MBRANDID
                                     , tpb1.BRANDDESC
                                     , tpmb1.MBRANDDESC
                                     , tptech1.TECHNOLOGYDESC
                                     , tppb1.PRICEBAND
                                     , tpll1.LINELAUNCHDESC
                                     , tpc1.COMFORTDESC
                                     , tpcon1.CONSTRUCTDESC
                                     , tppc1.PRICECOLLECTIONDESC
                                     , ts1.SIZEID
                                     , ts1.DIMENSIONS
                                     , ts1.EBCPANELLENGTH
                                     , ts1.EBCPANELWIDTH
                                     , ts1.ACTIVE
                                   )
                         )    as ITEM_HIERARCHY_HASH_KEY
          from
             dbo.TSIPHITEM                 tpi1
              left join
                  dbo.TSIPHBASEITEM        tpbi1
              on
                  tpi1.BASEITEMID = tpbi1.BASEITEMID
              left join
                  dbo.TSIPHGROUP           tpg1
              on
                  tpbi1.PGCID = tpg1.PGCID
              left join
                  dbo.TSIPHLEVEL           tpl1
              on
                  tpg1.PLEVELID = tpl1.PLEVELID
              left join
                  dbo.TSIPHYEAROVERYEAR    tpyoy1
              on
                  tpl1.YOYID = tpyoy1.YOYID
              left join
                  dbo.TSIPHTYPE            tpt1
              on
                  tpyoy1.TYPEID = tpt1.TYPEID
              left join
                  dbo.TSIPHSTYLE           tps1
              on
                  tpt1.STYLEID = tps1.STYLEID
              left join
                  dbo.TSIPHBRAND           tpb1
              on
                  tps1.BRANDID = tpb1.BRANDID
              left join
                  dbo.TSIPHMASTERBRAND     tpmb1
              on
                  tpb1.MBRANDID = tpmb1.MBRANDID
              left join
                  dbo.TSIPHTECHNOLOGY      tptech1
              on
                  tpt1.TECHNOLOGYID = tptech1.TECHNOLOGYID
              left join
                  dbo.TSIPHPRICEBAND       tppb1
              on
                  tpyoy1.PRICEBANDID = tppb1.PRICEBANDID
              left join
                  dbo.TSIPHLINELAUNCH      tpll1
              on
                  tpl1.LINELAUNCHID = tpll1.LINELAUNCHID
              left join
                  dbo.TSIPHCOMFORT         tpc1
              on
                  tpg1.COMFORTID = tpc1.COMFORTID
              left join
                  dbo.TSIPHCONSTRUCTION    tpcon1
              on
                  tpg1.CONSTRUCTID = tpcon1.CONSTRUCTID
              left join
                  dbo.TSIPHPRICECOLLECTION tppc1
              on
                  tpbi1.PRICECOLLECTIONID = tppc1.PRICECOLLECTIONID
              left join
                  dbo.TPSSIZE              ts1
              on
                  tpi1.PRODSIZE = ts1.SIZECODE
     )                         brand1
     on
         it1.ITEMID = brand1.DISPLAYPRODUCTNUMBER
 Where
    it1.dataareaid <> '761'

select
it1.DATAAREAID
,it1.ITEMID
,it1.PRODUCT
,it1.ABCVALUE
,it1.COSTGROUPID
,it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION
,it1.CREATEDDATETIME
,it1.MODIFIEDDATETIME
,da1.TIMEZONE as DATAAREA_TIMEZONE
,e1.PRODUCT as ECORESPRODUCTTRANSLATION_PRODUCT
,e1.NAME as ECORESPRODUCTTRANSLATION_NAME
,e1.MODIFIEDDATETIME as ECORESPRODUCTTRANSLATION_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,bcg1.DATAAREAID as BOMCOSTGROUP_DATAAREAID
,bcg1.COSTGROUPID as BOMCOSTGROUP_COSTGROUPID
,bcg1.NAME as BOMCOSTGROUP_NAME
,bcg1.COSTGROUPBEHAVIOR as BOMCOSTGROUP_COSTGROUPBEHAVIOR
,bcg1.COSTGROUPTYPE as BOMCOSTGROUP_COSTGROUPTYPE
,bcg1.TYPEDEFAULT as BOMCOSTGROUP_TYPEDEFAULT
,E_CATEGORY as DEFAULTDIMENSION_E_CATEGORY
,E_CATEGORY_DESCRIPTION_PARENT as DEFAULTDIMENSION_E_CATEGORY_DESCRIPTION_PARENT
,E_CATEGORY_DESCRIPTION as DEFAULTDIMENSION_E_CATEGORY_DESCRIPTION
,F_FAMILY as DEFAULTDIMENSION_F_FAMILY
,F_FAMILY_DESCRIPTION as DEFAULTDIMENSION_F_FAMILY_DESCRIPTION
,DEFAULTDIMENSION_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,tzi1.TIMEZONEID as TIMEZONEINFO_TIMEZONEID
,tzi1.STARTDATE as TIMEZONEINFO_STARTDATE
,tzi1.ENDDATE as TIMEZONEINFO_ENDDATE
,tzi1.TIMEBIAS as TIMEZONEINFO_TIMEBIAS
,itm1.MODULETYPE as INVENTTABLEMODULE_MODULETYPE
,itm1.DATAAREAID as INVENTTABLEMODULE_DATAAREAID
,itm1.ITEMID as INVENTTABLEMODULE_ITEMID
,itm1.UNITID as INVENTTABLEMODULE_UNITID
,uom1.RECID as UNITOFMEASURE_RECID
,uom1.SYMBOL as UNITOFMEASURE_SYMBOL
,uom1.MODIFIEDDATETIME as UNITOFMEASURE_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,uomt1.UNITOFMEASURE as UNITOFMEASURETRANSLATION_UNITOFMEASURE
,uomt1.DESCRIPTION as UNITOFMEASURETRANSLATION_DESCRIPTION
,uomt1.MODIFIEDDATETIME as UNITOFMEASURETRANSLATION_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,null as TSIPHITEM_DISPLAYPRODUCTNUMBER
,null as TSIPHITEM_BASEITEMID
,null as TSIPHITEM_PRODSIZE
,null as TSIPHBASEITEM_PGCID
,null as TSIPHBASEITEM_BASEITEMDESCRIPTION
,null as TSIPHBASEITEM_DEFAULTFDNHIGH
,null as TSIPHBASEITEM_DEFAULTFDNLOW
,null as TSIPHBASEITEM_DEFAULTFDNMED
,null as TSIPHBASEITEM_PIECETYPEID
,null as TSIPHBASEITEM_PRICECOLLECTIONID
,null as TSIPHGROUP_PLEVELID
,null as TSIPHGROUP_PGCDESC
,null as TSIPHGROUP_ISACTIVE
,null as TSIPHGROUP_EFFECTIVEDATE
,null as TSIPHGROUP_EXPIRATIONDATE
,null as TSIPHGROUP_MSTRPGCID
,null as TSIPHGROUP_COMFORTID
,null as TSIPHGROUP_CONSTRUCTID
,null as TSIPHLEVEL_LINELAUNCHID
,null as TSIPHLEVEL_YOYID
,null as TSIPHLEVEL_PLEVELDESC
,null as TSIPHLEVEL_ISACTIVE
,null as TSIPHLEVEL_ISSPECIALTY
,null as TSIPHYEAROVERYEAR_TYPEID
,null as TSIPHYEAROVERYEAR_PRICEBANDID
,null as TSIPHYEAROVERYEAR_YOYDESC
,null as TSIPHTYPE_STYLEID
,null as TSIPHTYPE_TECHNOLOGYID
,null as TSIPHTYPE_TYPEDESC
,null as TSIPHSTYLE_BRANDID
,null as TSIPHSTYLE_STYLEDESC
,null as TSIPHBRAND_MBRANDID
,null as TSIPHBRAND_BRANDDESC
,null as TSIPHMASTERBRAND_MBRANDDESC
,null as TSIPHTECHNOLOGY_TECHNOLOGYDESC
,null as TSIPHPRICEBAND_PRICEBAND
,null as TSIPHLINELAUNCH_LINELAUNCHDESC
,null as TSIPHCOMFORT_COMFORTDESC
,null as TSIPHCONSTRUCTION_CONSTRUCTDESC
,null as TSIPHPRICECOLLECTION_PRICECOLLECTIONDESC
,null as TPSSIZE_SIZEID
,null as TPSSIZE_DIMENSIONS
,null as TPSSIZE_EBCPANELLENGTH
,null as TPSSIZE_EBCPANELWIDTH
, null as TPSSIZE_ACTIVE
, null as ITEMGROUPID
, null as ITEMGROUPNAME
,(SELECT MAX(LastUpdateDate)
FROM (VALUES (it1.MODIFIEDDATETIME),
(isnull(e1.MODIFIEDDATETIME, '1950-01-01')),
(isnull(uom1.MODIFIEDDATETIME, '1950-01-01')),
(isnull(uomt1.MODIFIEDDATETIME, '1950-01-01'))) AS UpdateDate(LastUpdateDate)) AS LAST_MODIFIEDDATETIME
,null as ITEM_HIERARCHY_HASH_KEY
,1 as BRAND_RANK
from
dbo.INVENTTABLE it1
left join (select d10.ID, d10.TIMEZONE
			from dbo.DATAAREA d10
			inner join (select ID, max(RECID) as MAX_RECID
						from dbo.DATAAREA
						group by ID) d11 on
				d10.ID = d11.ID and
				d10.RECID = d11.MAX_RECID
			) da1 on
	it1.DATAAREAID = da1.ID
left join (select e10.PRODUCT, e10.NAME, e10.MODIFIEDDATETIME
			from dbo.ECORESPRODUCTTRANSLATION e10
			inner join (select PRODUCT, max(MODIFIEDDATETIME) as MAX_MODIFIEDDATETIME
						from dbo.ECORESPRODUCTTRANSLATION
						where LANGUAGEID = 'en-us'
						group by PRODUCT) e11 on
				e10.PRODUCT = e11.PRODUCT and
				e10.MODIFIEDDATETIME = e11.MAX_MODIFIEDDATETIME
			where LANGUAGEID = 'en-us') e1 on
	it1.PRODUCT = e1.PRODUCT
left join dbo.BOMCOSTGROUP bcg1 on
	it1.DATAAREAID = bcg1.DATAAREAID and
	it1.COSTGROUPID = bcg1.COSTGROUPID
left join (select distinct it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION
				, max(
					case when da1.NAME = 'E_Category' then davsi1.DISPLAYVALUE
						else null
						end
					) over (partition by it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION) as E_CATEGORY
				, max(
					case when da1.NAME = 'F_Family' then davsi1.DISPLAYVALUE
						else null
						end
					) over (partition by it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION) as F_FAMILY
				
				, max(
					case when da1.NAME = 'E_Category' and davsi1.DISPLAYVALUE in ('10', '11', '20', '50', '60') then desc1.DESCRIPTION
						when da1.NAME = 'E_Category' then 'Other'
					else null
					end
					) over (partition by it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION) as E_CATEGORY_DESCRIPTION_PARENT
				-- use MIN because you want the first iteration of the character set
				, min(
					case when da1.NAME = 'E_Category' then desc1.DESCRIPTION
					else null
					end
					) over (partition by it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION) as E_CATEGORY_DESCRIPTION
				, min(
					case when da1.NAME = 'F_Family' then desc1.DESCRIPTION
					else null
					end
					) over (partition by it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION) as F_FAMILY_DESCRIPTION
				, max(
					(select max(i) from (values (davsi1.MODIFIEDDATETIME), (dav1.MODIFIEDDATETIME), (da1.MODIFIEDDATETIME), (desc1.DESC_MODIFIEDDATETIME)) AS T(i))
					) over (partition by it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION) as DEFAULTDIMENSION_MODIFIEDDATETIME
			from (select distinct DEFAULTDIMENSION from dbo.INVENTTABLE) it1
			left join dbo.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESETITEM davsi1 on
				it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION = davsi1.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESET
			left join dbo.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE dav1 on
				davsi1.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE = dav1.RECID
			left join dbo.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE da1 on
				dav1.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE = da1.RECID
			left join (select dft1.VALUE, da2.NAME, dft1.DESCRIPTION
							, (select max(i) from (values (dft1.MODIFIEDDATETIME), (dadc1.MODIFIEDDATETIME), (da2.MODIFIEDDATETIME)) AS T(i)) as DESC_MODIFIEDDATETIME
						from dbo.DIMENSIONFINANCIALTAG dft1
						left join dbo.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEDIRCATEGORY dadc1 on
							dft1.FINANCIALTAGCATEGORY = dadc1.DIRCATEGORY
						left join dbo.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE da2 on
							dadc1.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE = da2.RECID) desc1 on
				davsi1.DISPLAYVALUE = desc1.VALUE and
				da1.NAME = desc1.NAME
			) def1 on
	it1.DEFAULTDIMENSION = def1.DEFAULTDIMENSION
left join dbo.TIMEZONEINFO tzi1 on
	da1.TIMEZONE = tzi1.TIMEZONEID and
	it1.CREATEDDATETIME >= tzi1.STARTDATE and
	it1.CREATEDDATETIME < tzi1.ENDDATE
left join dbo.INVENTTABLEMODULE itm1 on
	itm1.MODULETYPE = 1 and
	it1.DATAAREAID = itm1.DATAAREAID and
	it1.ITEMID = itm1.ITEMID
left join (select uom10.RECID, uom10.SYMBOL, uom10.MODIFIEDDATETIME
			from dbo.UNITOFMEASURE uom10
			inner join (select SYMBOL, max(MODIFIEDDATETIME) as MAX_MODIFIEDDATETIME
						from dbo.UNITOFMEASURE
						group by SYMBOL) uom11 on
				uom10.SYMBOL = uom11.SYMBOL and
				uom10.MODIFIEDDATETIME = uom11.MAX_MODIFIEDDATETIME) uom1 on
	itm1.UNITID = uom1.SYMBOL
left join (select uomt10.UNITOFMEASURE, uomt10.DESCRIPTION, uomt10.MODIFIEDDATETIME
			from dbo.UNITOFMEASURETRANSLATION uomt10
			inner join (select UNITOFMEASURE, max(MODIFIEDDATETIME) as MAX_MODIFIEDDATETIME
						from dbo.UNITOFMEASURETRANSLATION
						where LANGUAGEID = 'en-us'
						group by UNITOFMEASURE) uomt11 on
				uomt10.UNITOFMEASURE = uomt11.UNITOFMEASURE and
				uomt10.MODIFIEDDATETIME = uomt11.MAX_MODIFIEDDATETIME
			where uomt10.LANGUAGEID = 'en-us') uomt1 on
	uom1.RECID = uomt1.UNITOFMEASURE
where it1.dataareaid = '761'
